{"tid":1021412,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一直有心儀女同事，以為老細今日比咗500蚊係鼓勵我去馬，點知…","createTime":"2019-02-14T08:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T08:52:00.000Z","uid":154872,"like":1718,"dislike":127,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"7b2a2d38c1b34aaa7ae4ee9ebf3ca78a737a396d","tid":1021412,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:38:04.000Z","msg":"話說我同老細佢地成班男人放工都會去happy hour，傾開計佢地都知我對其中一個單身女同事啊Jane好有意思，咁佢地都一直叫我去馬唔好等。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日情人節，本來已經想同啊Jane表白，一返到公司我老細好急咁行過，仲笑笑口咁比咗張500蚊我同講咗句&rdquo;加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &rdquo;，嗰刻我直頭想喊，覺得老細真係好似我大哥咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，然後我即刻落街買咗束細細地嘅花打算放工送比啊Jane。點知啱啱3點幾嗰陣老細打比我問我做乜冇用嗰500蚊幫佢部車加油，佢部車喺新界嗰邊跪低咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。佢而家搭的士去見客，要我放工OT自己去幫佢搞返掂部車，我公司喺港島...屌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d10a4dd9a09e88518fdcdc0ca234c426b9d7be","tid":1021412,"uid":1585,"like":476,"dislike":4,"score":472,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:39:05.000Z","msg":"轉貼請注明出處"},{"pid":"7e2fa3059fbd2b9bb0a1b7d508ae2508c0ac2b4c","tid":1021412,"uid":196924,"like":153,"dislike":1,"score":152,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:39:36.000Z","msg":"你腦細係支那狗?"},{"pid":"24c6fefc91b48cb0babe12f47169c598e4413556","tid":1021412,"uid":139228,"like":106,"dislike":1,"score":105,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:39:37.000Z","msg":"Dear Jane<br />\n<br />\nYou suck!"},{"pid":"6dc5281a3ff69bc7b02ab63a76fe8e3d22ed78e4","tid":1021412,"uid":35746,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:40:08.000Z","msg":"起底，樓主d幽默感真係。。。"},{"pid":"629afb800d1d5125d5bd1f6ddcd112afb2391c99","tid":1021412,"uid":156376,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:41:52.000Z","msg":"唔好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955157c89542